{
  "stem": "11000.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because it wasn't-- so we had some money, just in case, you know, when we come back, that we have something again to get started with.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so we really didn't think serious anything about going there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A lot of people went into hiding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had an opportunity also, the four of us, by good friends who wanted to hide us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The problem was that nobody was able to take four people in one household.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we had to split up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the way it was presented was that my dad and I were supposed to go with one family, my mother and my sister with another family.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "These people were good people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Don't forget, food was rationed already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we, of course, wouldn't get any coupons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So they had to share what they got with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this way, 8,000 people were saved that way in Holland during that period.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "However, my parents decided since we were not allowed to know where the other two were, and that was done-- the underground, you know, it was a dangerous assignment-- just in case one of us would get caught.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they would force us to tell them where the others are.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So therefore, we were not supposed to know where, let's say, my father and I weren't supposed to know where my mother and sister were.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later of course, my parents decided against.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I felt they don't want to break up the family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if we have to go, so we'll go like the rest of them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, after all, the same thing-- we are still young.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we'll survive it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's no problem.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sure enough, one day, we were-- they came to the house, like 1:00, midnight.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
